Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Demo tapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A way for composers and performers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to convey their musical image to a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, the demo tape of a new song by TWO-MIX,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,holds a big secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:22.16,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a glittering galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:25.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts dried by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:29.21,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's case has a crazy secret\Nbehind a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:15.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Genta, Mitsuhiko, Ayumi, and I\Nwere playing Kick-the-Can,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:18.24,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but soon found ourselves having lunch at a restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:22.37,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}with Two-Mix vocalist, Minami Takayama{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:29.86,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She had snuck out to look for her missing partner, Shiina Nagano{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:37.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But at the restaurant, she was kidnapped before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:43.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The kidnappers demanded\Nthe bag she left at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:48.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's more, they demanded that {\i1}we{\i0} take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:53.33,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It appeared they were after a Two-Mix demo tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:58.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After taking the bag as ordered, the kidnappers contacted us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:04.43,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and said to lose the officers and have Ayumi deliver the tape alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:09.25,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't put Ayumi in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, I devised a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} switched places?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My word...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnappers are after the demo tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said to have Ayumi deliver it\Nand to lose the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...so Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} switched with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why didn't you tell us you switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd be most off guard if we let them think their plan worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said we couldn't let anyone know until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, now we can't locate the kidnappers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he said that these Tracking Glasses should—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Conan's gonna get all the credit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can still find their hideout and then tell the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, after we've saved Two-Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Detective Boys Save the Day!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK! Let's go catch those kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you shouting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we were saying, "Oh! We're so hungry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... We were saying, "Oh! We're so hungry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're off to buy some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come back quickly, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:05:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We're so hungry! We're so hungry!\NWe're so hungry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.24,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As agreed, it looks like you came alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, bring the tape up to the second floor of the nearby warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your beloved Two-Mix is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't be needing you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say your prayers while you still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought it, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're you—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's the guy from the coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to contact the police for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a phone booth over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1-1-9...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! That's the fire department!\NThe police is 110!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't you need to press this button?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.45,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is 110.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, Inspector Megure, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:35.29,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello? Where'd you go, little boy? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.47,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you find us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told to bring this tape here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they really questioned us\Nabout where the tape was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would they want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's save the details for after we've escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the police are on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're on their way here right now,\Nusing my Tracking Glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It homes in on this badge's transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan Edogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry before the other kidnapper comes back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are those your "Tracking Glasses"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I caught 'em snooping around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiots! Why didn't you give the glasses to the police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have plenty of time to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm nice enough to turn you into ashes. Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! At least tell us why you kidnapped us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ask Buddha in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The countdown bell sounds..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"and says to change hearts and run."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It rings once, twice..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Like the sound of off-season fireworks..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Like the sound of someone, somewhere, confessing their love..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You damn kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. The lyrics on the Two-Mix demo tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the reason you kidnapped Two-Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Satoshi Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The night of New Year's Eve,\Nyou killed a man near Shoenji Temple
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and were investigated by Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,New Year's Eve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where we came up with that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:09:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a murder near that temple\Nwhen the bell rang at 11:50...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the man died holding the gun,\Nhad gunpowder on his hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there was an empty shell in the barrel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the police believed your claim\Nthat it went off during your struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the gun-toting maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that wasn't actually the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had brought the gun\Nto kill him from the very start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After shooting him through the heart with the first shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you loaded another bullet into the barrel and fired at the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with his hand on the gun, to leave behind traces of gunpowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no witnesses around, so while you called the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the man sleeping outside was to run off\Nwith the extra bullet and shell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to put you in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there were people who heard those sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You two from Two-Mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "countdown bell" was the New Year's bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two fireworks were the two gunshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the line, "1996 just flew right by,"\Nindicated the year it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Add in Shoenji Temple,\Nwhich you mentioned on the radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the time and place\Nof the gunshots becomes clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assume you heard the radio show the demo tape was played on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you kidnapped Two-Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to get rid of the tape and them before the police found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm Satoshi Miyahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy I killed was an old bank-robbing partner of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He suddenly threatened\Nto tell the cops, so I offed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have just run off after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A temple priest had seen my face while I was on my way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luckily, he was hard of hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Said he had to stay at the temple to ring the bell, so I let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never expected someone to hear the shots and make a song about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cell phone, huh? Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is that long-haired guy's phone\NI had my partner hold onto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, can't be careless around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even if you did call the police,\Nyou'd die before they get here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, please enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector Megure. I let them and those kids go unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd. He didn't even mention Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} switching places...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector. I just got word on the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that some kids had called 110 and asked for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! When?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, some 15 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't they tell us sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They didn't state their emergency,\Nso the operator thought it was a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do we know the location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was too short to trace...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad! If the kidnappers were the ones who hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use! It's not budging!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}OK! Time for my Power Kick Shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ow! It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you kids OK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad! At this rate, we won't survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't breathe the smoke! Get lower to the—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those annoying cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Quit—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:57.40,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yay! We're long gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.25,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're calling from a police box!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.39,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}See for yourself if you don't believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did they get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See! Told you this Earring Cell Phone was useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We can still get to the concert in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiina{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mock me, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill each one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}- Bastard!\N- Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was awesome, Minami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}10 minutes later, a fire truck arrived with police cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:25.62,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the two-man gang was put under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:31.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Naturally, the Detective Boys\Ngot a harsh scolding,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:36.26,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but Minami Takayama{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}\Nstuck up for us, so we were acquitted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:40.24,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and then we rushed to the Budokan\Nin Inspector Megure's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already 30 minutes past!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not good. The crowd's getting antsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to go change, so wait backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wanna introduce you to everyone later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is Minami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} still not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez! What's she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Is this backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! You're not allowed back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told us to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Minami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK! Put the opening song on standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Someone go to the dressing rooms\Nand ask how much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what does this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! The song's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do?! They're not here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?! They'd get even madder if we did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm figuring that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, do you have this song's lyrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yeah, they're in that CD case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what do you want them for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,BREAK MY LIES
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"kakedasu senaka o oikakete mou ichido..."\N{\c}Chase after me again as I rush off
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SAVE MY HEART!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"hontou wa matteru ...dakishimete..."\N{\c}I'm actually waiting... Embrace me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ima RETURN TO LOVE...\N{\c}Now return to love
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could swear I've heard that singing voice before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't joke like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell's singing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about off-key...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it is Takayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bad idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"tatta hito-koto" ga sunao ni iezu ni kizutsuketa yo\N{\c}It hurt that I couldn't say that one little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nakitai-kurai ni nukumori kono te ni motomenagara...\N{\c}as I sought this warm hand almost in tears
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,keiken fuereba yume mo\N{\c}And with every new experience
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,mujaki ni mirenaku naru-kara...\N{\c}I find it harder to dream in innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sore de mo dokoka de kitto shinjitakute mitsumeteta...\N{\c}Even so, I searched because I still believed deep down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,BREAK MY LIES
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:19:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"hitomi ni yureteru shinjitsu ni kidzuite..."\N{\c}Realize the quivering truth in my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SAVE MY HEART!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"furueru kuchibiru kuchidzukete..."\N{\c}Kiss these trembling lips
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ima RETURN TO LOVE...\N{\c}Now return to love
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,soba ni iru-toki kanjite ita no wa yowasa ja naku\N{\c}What I felt when I was with you wasn't weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,jibun ni tarinai nanika o oginau-you na yasuragi\N{\c}It was a kind of serenity that made up for something I lacked
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,daiji na mono-hodo itsuka\N{\c}The more important the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ushinau itami ga kowakute\N{\c}the more afraid I am to lose them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hitogomi no naka de hitori... kaeru basho o sagashiteta...\N{\c}All alone in the crowd, I searched for a place to return to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,BREAK MY LIES
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"kotoba ni dekinai setsunasa o ubatte..."\N{\c}Snatch away the pain I can't put into words
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:20:02.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}And so the Two-Mix concert that we barged into ended without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SAVE MY HEART!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"doko ni mo ikenai ...sono mune ni..."\N{\c}I've nowhere to go... Trapped in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ima RETURN TO LOVE...\N{\c}Now return to love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what did you think of singing on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet! Just once, and you're hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what did the little detective think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was the concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. It was OK, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so cheeky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, this is your dressing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector! Can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to ask when you're so exhausted,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I was hoping you could come to the station to give a statement...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, take your time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a wonderful concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is for saving us today! Practice at home, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And some for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I get autographs and pictures, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready?! What's 1 plus 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:19.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Karaoke Box"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Break my lies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chase after me again as I rush off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all he's been singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he hasn't gotten any better...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm actually waiting... Embrace me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now return to love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Return to love
